{"tid":1497459,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8·23 香港之路唔好圍威喂","createTime":"2019-08-23T03:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:57:32.000Z","uid":276788,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3043540f8e003781cee9e6b14362a9f549d0c6b4","tid":1497459,"uid":276788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">今晚係一個大好機會做文宣!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n見到眼望望嘅路人甲<br />\n唔好怕醜 同佢地傾下計<br />\n特別係啲<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">公公婆婆</span></span><br />\n佢地平時都唔知班人阻街遊行做乜9<br />\n所以淨係聽tbb講我地係暴徒<br />\n今晚係時候話比佢地知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我 地 2 個 月 黎 做 緊 乜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">step 1: 關心了解</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅一步<br />\n好似仔女咁同佢傾下計<br />\n最起碼過咗今晚<br />\n佢會覺得<span style=\"color: maroon;\">黑衫係好人唔係暴徒</span><br />\n孝順敬老知書達禮<br />\n<br />\n以下為世界通用傾計開場白:<br />\n食咗飯未<br />\n今日點呀<br />\n我呀婆同你差唔多年輕<br />\n<br />\n搵下common topic, 耐心啲聽佢講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">step 2: 邀請參與</span></span><br />\n<br />\n傾計進行得順利<br />\n就可以試下問<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">&ldquo;過黎一齊拖住傾呀&rdquo;</span><br />\n有身體接觸可以令人更<span style=\"color: maroon;\">相信對方</span><br />\n<br />\n*<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果佢有咩恐懼擔憂就唔好迫佢</span>*<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">step 3: 到佢了解我地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n關心完就係時候<span style=\"color: maroon;\">文宣</span>啦<br />\n唔好轉得咁突然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有機會入就問句<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">&ldquo;最近有冇睇新聞呀&rdquo;</span><br />\n之後內容就自行按情況調整<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">step 4: 拉票拉票</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果一切順利<br />\n佢聽到心服口服<br />\n你可以順手幫11月拉個靚票<br />\n完滿結束<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係好多活動可以咁多時間<span style=\"color: blue;\">接觸到街坊</span><br />\n好好珍惜今次機會<br />\n平時佢地最多攞張傳單就走<br />\n今次要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>大大力</strong></span></span>比街坊了解我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>爭取非同溫層嘅支持</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 6月9之後先開始睇連登嘅p牌仔 求幫推"},{"pid":"3dec02ca64961427058a168dcf63df3a43e21f12","tid":1497459,"uid":119454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"直4輕推"},{"pid":"73b80b92ec98581704079985174ef8ef1950cad9","tid":1497459,"uid":284529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"「8.23香港之路」集合點出席人數估算<br />\n<br />\n1. 已報名人士請準時七點出席。 <br />\n2. 統計結果只供事前參考，實際落場未必有相同人數，請睇嘅手足請自行決定，亦請相信香港人集體智慧。<br />\n3. Google Form將於下午5時前停止更新 <br />\n4. 現場最新消息將以TG channel 及 FB 為準<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdn8obEeNEp4bN-uOJ95qL1tckBql7WIJ5poZR6Xa4BF9hG8w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdn8obEeNEp4bN-uOJ95qL1tckBql7WIJ5poZR6Xa4BF9hG8w%2Fviewform&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1fulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=dd1ddec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdn8obEeNEp4bN-uOJ95qL1tckBql7WIJ5poZR6Xa4BF9hG8w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">登記無須填寫個人資料 , 可以參考統計結果選擇去未滿人既集合點<br />\n<br />\n現時 荃灣,旺角,觀塘,中環 都超級爆人 , 有心人可考慮其他集合點 , 多謝</span></span>"},{"pid":"98e16c25ebba0211f2905eec46af48daf27bd0ca","tid":1497459,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好"},{"pid":"c155ccecfeb5251290b5a55f6ce3e0f279f695d8","tid":1497459,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"要大肆宣傳set 一個dea